                  <provenance>
                     <p>RSPA 1-118 were presented to the
                                                  Royal Society in January 1792 by Sir William and
                                                  Lady Jones.</p>
                     <p>According to the Wilkins
                                                  Catalogue, MS RSPA 83 was presented by Lady
                                                  Jones.</p>
                     <p>The Royal Society's collection of 280
                                                  Persian and Arabic, and 86 Sanskrit manuscripts
                                                  were transferred to the India Office Library in
                                                  1876.</p>
                  </provenance>
